snippet: Casey Janssen had spent his entire big league career with the Toronto Blue Jays, going 29-24 with 90 saves and a 3.52 E.R.A. since 2006.
abstract: Washington Nationals sign right-handed reliever Casey Janssen to one-year, $5 million contract; other baseball news noted.
